  "text": "Phenotypic characteristics, i.e. colony morphology, color and growth rate on prepared slides were studied by means of microscopic observations. The potato dextrose agar (PDA) is used for the cultivation of fungi. Isolated spores were examined to complement the phylogenetic analysis using the taxonomic for Aspergillus [CITATION_1] .",
